name: feh

variants.name: build_system
variants.description: Build systems supported by the package

description:
feh is an X11 image viewer aimed mostly at console users. Unlike most
other viewers, it does not have a fancy GUI, but simply displays images.
It is controlled via commandline arguments and configurable key/mouse
actions.

dependencies.name: gmake
dependencies.description:
GNU Make is a tool which controls the generation of executables and
other non-source files of a program from the program's source files.

dependencies.name: imlib2
dependencies.description:
Library that does image file loading and saving as well as rendering,
manipulation, arbitrary polygon support
